data.name: Mirror World Token
data.description:
MW (Mirror World Token) is described to be a file system combining blockchain and distributed storage technology, which constructs a Global Multi Chain deployment distributed storage ecosystem with high security, high privacy and high availability. The purpose of this system is to provide high quality and low price file storage services, and to build an easy-to-use and available distributed storage application.
